and
other
movable
property
excluding
automobiles
,
nineteen
said
that
they
did
and
twenty
that
they
did
not
.

One
assessor
checked
boats
only
,
another
trailers
and
tractors
,
one
mentioned
house
trailers
,
and
two
others
referred
to
trailers
without
