activated
sludge
system
.

The
retention
period
in
the
aerated
lagoon
ranged
from
9.8
to
2.6
days
,
averaging
6.4
days
.

The
average
volatile
suspended
solids
in
the
effluent
was
75
while
MLSS
averaged
170
volatile
suspended
solids
.

The
oxygen
uptake
rate
in
the
mixed
liquor
averaged
0.8
during
the
first
